      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration at one load rate (5 mm/min displacement control). Although the protocol is the regulatory standard, only one test condition was evaluated; no variation in load rate, offset distance, or environmental condition was explored. Achieved level 2 against a required level 3 for model risk level 3, representing a gap that was noted in the assessment but not adjudicated as blocking given the mandatory nature of the F1717 protocol."
